Anthony F. Earley Jr.
Executive Compensation
As Chairman, Chief Executive Officer, and President, PG&E Corporation at PG&E CORP, Anthony F. Earley Jr. made $10,845,074 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,318,750 was received as a salary, $1,928,672 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $7,500,072 was awarded as stock and $97,580 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


